DESCRIPTION:RAYE has partnered with PLUS1 so that $1 per ticket supports or
	ganizations bringing hope to communities and advancing equity\, access\, a
	nd dignity for all - including Ripples Charity\, which works in Ghana to p
	rovide education\, training\, and healthcare programs that help people bui
	ld sustainable livelihoods. www.plus1.org All support acts are subject to 
	change without notice. There are no refunds or exchanges. There is no re-e
	ntry into the venue once exited. All patrons require a ticket\, regardless
